---
description: Keep site work within the approved corporate handoff and evidence gates
alwaysApply: true
---

For an active site program, read the corporate handoff before editing. Site specialists
implement as root-dispatched, nondelegating workers; the root runs gate commands; operations
excellence reviews immutable root-produced evidence. Use isolated workspaces for independent
writers. Do not alter corporate approvals, weaken tests, infer gate success, or grant user
approval.
